== a missing command with a slash exits 127:
shit: exec: '/nonexistent/cmd': not found
rc=127
== a missing command on the PATH exits 127:
shit: exec: 'nonexistent_cmd_xyz': not found
rc=127
== a non-executable file exits 126:
shit: Unable to execute 'TMPDIR/notexec' because Permission denied
rc=126
== exec replaces the shell and runs the command:
replaced
== exec in a command substitution runs as a child:
[sub]
